Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.19,0:01:31.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,步数
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟  这不是高木同学吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.04,0:01:42.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能在这里遇到  真巧呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我知道你会经过这里
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我假装这是偶然  向她发起比试的话
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是高木同学也发现不了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一定会赢
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你去哪里啊  西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是随便转转而已
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么事还到这种地方  真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.74,0:02:21.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,总之偶遇也是种缘分  跟我比试比试吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.16,0:02:22.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比什么
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,先假装思考一下
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后装作突然想到的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,估算走到那棵树需要的步数
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,更接近答案的人算赢怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,到那边的电线杆怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没 可以的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来这招吗  高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我早猜到会这样
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,已经数好到电线杆要走多少步了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是听高木同学的推测
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一个更接近答案的步数就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于能赢过高木同学了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这并不是耍赖
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,决定到电线杆的可是高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,还是到第二根电线杆那里吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也不是不行
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样决定了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,到第一根电线杆要走35步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,粗略算作两倍的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那70步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  为什么算得那么准
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那72步
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那走咯
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.53,0:03:51.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 5 6…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.63,0:04:04.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,32 33 34 35 36 37 38…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,第一根就超过了35步
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  因为要配合高木同学的步子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样能赢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  西片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你遇到我真的是偶然吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你明明不知道我要去哪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比试中走的却是我要去的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为计划超级完美  居然漏了这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  你其实知道我要去哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后特意在这里等我的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 西片啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不就变成跟踪狂了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 就是偶然啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,方向也是随便选的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真可疑啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个了 接着比吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶紧的话 你的约定就…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我和人约好了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然知道啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  西片你…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,跟踪狂…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,都假装偶遇来见我了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 是来和你比试的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  刚数到多少步了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,20步左右
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不对啊  虽然我也不记得了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也没时间了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的比试就作废吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这次能赢的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我明天就和家人去旅游了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是之前因为日期跟你妈那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜托我妈提前去了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想要什么土特产啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓  什么都可以
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回来再见吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,又没能赢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呀嗬
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等很久了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上什么开心事了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,有点
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.47,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz30.12\frx4\fry358\pos(1370,1032)}我的表姐来我家住
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,和美奈的眉毛一模一样诶
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你表姐是高中生吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.36,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(516,1054,572,218,3000,3200)\frx0\fry0\frz353.6}西瓜好好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我的问题啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,表姐…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.78,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx2\fry0\frz1.137\move(685.333,981.333,648,581.333,2020,2228)}想要什么样的土特产
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.78,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx4\fry0\pos(674,900)\frz0.3316}点心
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗也就这种时候回得快
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我都行
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你表姐…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.71,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(527.333,943.667)\frz355.8\frx358\fry2}喜欢能拿手里的还是不能拿手里的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能拿着和不能拿着的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,脑筋急转弯？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,到了这种时候反而慢了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.81,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(658,990)\frz359.7}打翻水桶了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,水桶？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是回答我的问题啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,放烟花吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等会再放
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,等会是什么时候啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了等会再放  我现在有点忙
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.55,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx2\fry2\pos(928,1031)\frz26.71}一起去看夏日祭的烟花吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 烟花啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗啊 又秒回了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那你表姐…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.93,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(922,850)\frz28.16\frx4\fry6}晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.93,Takagisan - screen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1744,786)\frz29.03\frx10\fry6}表…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得还是这么早啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日祭啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,去年是和冴一起去的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今年说了要和朋友一起去呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冴  放烟花吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  快点来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,心动心动
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呵  很好吃的喔
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,土特产
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你喜欢就好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…算了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去旅游了  这是土特产
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,点心吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.21,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,上当了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个点心虽然包装上没写
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其实能酸掉大牙
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.26,0:09:41.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,旅游的时候我一直在找吓高木同学一跳的土特产
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,找了很多家店  历尽千辛万苦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了这个
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是我今早刚买到的自信之礼
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你今天才刚旅游回来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就跑来把土特产送给我
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想见我呀
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是  我只是想把好不容易找到的土特产…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想立刻送给我对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再说下去  点心的事情会暴露的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这就回去了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事办完了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  总感觉…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要回去了  顺路去趟神社吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没见面了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.09,0:11:07.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为好久没见了吗  好紧张
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.14,0:11:08.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你往我这看了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才没看
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好羞耻
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为什么突然去神社
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你一起吃你送给我的土特产
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.58,0:11:35.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到高木同学被酸掉牙的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大好机会啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也挺好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:53.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片旅游的时候也想着我呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我有说错吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你还给我买了土特产呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…虽然是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但这话总觉得不太对
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还会立刻来见我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸又红了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.38,0:12:23.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  等到了神社…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说西片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我买土特产还送来给我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很开心
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那份土特产上没写
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实它很酸  你小心点
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道会是这么回事
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.69,0:13:28.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  但是等到了神社就让西片先吃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好酸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.21,0:13:42.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是让人吃了还想吃呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.38,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在不知情的情况下吃可能会吓一跳
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但很好吃哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,作战本身没问题
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是我提醒了她…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.14,0:13:55.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦  我会自己吃的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你脸红了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被夕阳照红的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.24,0:14:08.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之前在这里聊过天
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我因为旅行的事跟妈妈吵架那件事
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.17,0:14:19.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始本来预定要夏日祭那天去旅行的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  也就是你是和朋友有约在先吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片你要和谁一起去夏日祭呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还没定好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经空出行程了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明特地岔开了旅行的时间？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是某人来邀请我的话
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和他一起去
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个经常被我捉弄的某人
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.97,0:15:16.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,约定
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个背影是高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片  真巧啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…就是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道又是装作偶遇来见我了？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才不是啦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…因为这些东西看起来很重
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是来帮我的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.23,0:16:08.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,去钓鱼？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  和木村他们一起
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在海水浴的时节去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.32,0:16:18.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么说过了  但木村说钓鱼比较好
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那要和我一起去游泳吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们俩
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能去啦  都和木村他们约好了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  这些是？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭的食材
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想骑自行车去  但我忘记车子爆胎了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是糊涂啊高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片是不是也忘了什么啊？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了是指什么
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假作业做了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没做多少呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就光顾着玩了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学看起来已经做完了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我也还没做多少
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪有资格说我呀
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.89,0:17:21.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天一起去图书馆做作业吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样说好咯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,写完之后再去一趟神社吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你的自由研究要做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.29,0:17:53.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假里捉弄西片时的反应总结
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么做但是算了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的求你别做这个
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  还没决定好
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点决定好的话暑假就要结束了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  还剩一半呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,迷茫的话时间可就稍转即逝了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会稍转即逝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  之前的…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.49,0:19:04.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不  还是算了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  西片
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要进来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不了  我还约好了要去钓鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的答谢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.55,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…夏日祭…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.35,0:20:53.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.95,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也给你  还有这个  这个
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用给我这么多啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是下一条钓到大的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就邀请北条同学一起去夏日祭
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是钓到小的  就明天再邀请
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要去约她倒是已经决定好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是钓不到怎么办？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你钓鱼很菜
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就后天去邀请她
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂西片  我拿一罐果汁哦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  已经上钩了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.92,0:22:06.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan - text_cn,,0,0,0,,JP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:31.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,歩数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おっと  高木さんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:42.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こんな所で会うなんて偶然だね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,実は  ここを通るのは知っていたのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺が偶然を装い  勝負を挑もうとは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いくら高木さんでも気づくまい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日こそ  俺が勝つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…で  どこ行くの  西片は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,適当にブラブラしてただけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こんな所を用もないのに  珍しくない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そ  それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:21.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,とりあえず  偶然  会ったのも  何かの縁だし  勝負でもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:22.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何にする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,考えるフリを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そして  今  思いついたフリを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:31.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの木まで  何歩かかるか予想して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,近いほうが勝ちっていうのは  どう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それじゃ  ちょっと近いし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,向こうの電柱までにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そう来たか  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.52,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,計算どおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そう来るだろうと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あらかじめ  電柱までの歩数を数えておいたのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あとは高木さんの予想を聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それより正解に近い歩数を  言えばいいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ついに高木さんに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.16,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これはズルではない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,電柱までと決めたのは  高木さんなのだから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱり  2本先の電柱までにしよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.29,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な…  なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  ダメじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  決まりね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お…  落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1本目の電柱まで35歩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,単純に2倍すれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  70歩で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ  なんて  いい所をついてくるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  72歩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:51.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1  2  3  4  5  6…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1  2  3…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:04.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,32  33  34  35  36  37  38…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,1本目の電柱で35歩を超えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうか  高木さんの歩幅に合わせたせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これは勝てるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そういえば  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私に会ったのって  本当に偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうだけど  なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって  私の行き先  聞いてないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっちの方向で  勝負  仕掛けてきたから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,しまった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,完璧な作戦だと思ったのに  そんな盲点が…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.38,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして  私の行き先  知ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,わざわざ  ここで待ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な…  何のことやら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それってさ  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:50.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ストーカーというやつになるのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いやいや  偶然だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,行き先も  なんとなく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか怪しいなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それより  勝負の続きしようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,さっさとしないと  約束に…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんで  誰かと約束あるって知ってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,しまったー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やっぱり知ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それってさ  西片…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:14.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ストーカー…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私のこと好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,へっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって  そうでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,偶然装って  会いに来るんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:30.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ち…  違うよ  ただ勝負をしに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そういえば  今  何歩だっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.69,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,20歩くらい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,絶対違うよ  それ  覚えてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,時間もないし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この勝負  なしにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,しょうがない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  そういうことで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:52.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,勝てる勝負だったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.25,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,楽しかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうだ  私  あしたから家族旅行なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それって  確か  日にちのことで  お母さんと…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お願いして早めてもらったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.02,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お土産  何がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,べ…  別に  何でもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,帰ってきたら  また会おうね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また勝てなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ヤッホー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,待った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,何か  いいことあった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっとね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,花火
Comment: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ミナと眉毛が  そっくりね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:58.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,"いとこのお姉さんって  高校生"っと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早いな
Comment: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:06.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,質問に答えろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう1回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,"いとこのお姉さ"…
Comment: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早いな…
Comment: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,サナエも  こういうときだけ早い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私は何でもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.62,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,で  いとこの…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Comment: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,手に持つのと  持たないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なぞなぞ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,"何?"っと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ねえ  まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,待って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こういうときに限って  遅いし
Comment: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,バケツ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.19,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…ていうか  質問に答えろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ねえ  まだ  お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なぁに
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,花火しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あとにして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あとって  いつ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あとは  あとよ  今  ちょっと忙しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,チェッ
Comment: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なるほど  花火ね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,サナエだ  また早いな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,"了解"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…で  いとこの
Comment: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,相変わらず  寝るのは早いな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,夏祭りか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,去年はサエも一緒だったけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.57,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今年は友達と行くって言ってたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.12,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,サエ  花火しよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,やった  早く来て
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.67,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,キュンキュ〜ン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:56.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,フッ…  おいしウィーぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お土産
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.81,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,良かった  西片  喜んでくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.48,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ  いや  まあ  ありがとう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺も旅行に行ってたから  お土産
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:24.71,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お菓子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.54,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん  まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.21,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,かかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.51,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そのお菓子  パッケージには書いていないが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.88,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,とっても酸っぱいのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:41.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,旅行中  高木さんが驚くお土産を  ずっと探してたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,店という店を探しに探し  紆余曲折を経て
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.19,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ついに  これを見つけたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今朝  買ったばかりの自信の品だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片  今日  旅行から帰ってきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:00.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すぐに  お土産を渡しに来るなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.41,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなに  私に会いたかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.58,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,違うって  俺は  やっと見つけたお土産を…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,その…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すぐに渡したかったんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  そうなんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これ以上  言い訳したら  お菓子のことがバレてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  俺は  これで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もう帰るの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,用事は済んだし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに  なんだか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私も帰るから  神社でも寄ってかない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,会うの久しぶりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:07.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか  久しぶりだからか  緊張するというか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:08.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,別に何も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,こっち見てたでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,見てないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.36,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか恥ずかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早く帰りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.41,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,と…  ところで  なんで神社なんかに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.24,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片のお土産  一緒に食べようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ということは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:35.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんが  酸っぱそうにしている顔を  見られるってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ヒャッホ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.34,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すっごいチャンスだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:53.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片が  旅行中も私のこと考えてくれてて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:11:59.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だって  そうでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お土産  買ってきてくれたし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや…  そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:06.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なんか違う
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.50,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それに  すぐに  私に会いに来てくれるし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だから  それも違うって!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また顔赤いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:23.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,くそ…  神社に着きさえすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あのね  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.31,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お土産  買ってきてくれて  渡してくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントに  うれしいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.93,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そのお土産  書いてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,すごく酸っぱいから  気をつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そんなことだろうと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.15,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:28.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ううん  でも  神社  着いたら  まず  西片に食べてもらおうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ええっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,酸っぱ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:42.13,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…いけど  結構  クセになる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.38,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,知らないで食べたら  びっくりしたと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おいしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.01,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,作戦自体は悪くなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.39,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ネタばらしさえしなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:55.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あ〜ん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいよ  自分で食べるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,顔赤いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.78,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,夕日で  そう見えるだけだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.28,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,まったく  高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:08.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.74,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.91,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,前に  ここで話したこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ほら  旅行のことで  お母さんとケンカしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:19.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,最初の予定  夏祭りの日だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.42,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ああ  友達と約束があったってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片は  夏祭り  誰かと行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  別に決めてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:38.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,私も  予定  空けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.27,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,旅行ずらしてもらったのに?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.65,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,誰かさんが誘ってくれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一緒に行きたいなぁと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.79,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,よく  からかわれる誰かさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:16.72,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,約束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.06,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっちい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの後ろ姿は高木さんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片  奇遇だね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.96,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん…  そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.76,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,また偶然装って  会いに来たとか?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.18,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ち…  違うって!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの…  なんか重そうだから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.14,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,もしかして  手伝ってくれるとか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.56,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:08.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,釣り?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん  木村たちと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.86,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,この海水浴シーズンに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:18.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,俺も  そう言ったんだけど  木村が釣りがいいって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.62,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  私と泳ぎに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,2人っきりで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.80,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,行くわけないだろう  木村たちと約束したし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,それより  これ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,夕飯のお使い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.43,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自転車で行こうと思ったら  パンクしてるの忘れててさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.98,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ドジだね  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そういえば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片も忘れてることない?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.44,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,忘れてるって  何を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,夏休みの宿題  やってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.87,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あ〜  いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あんまりかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,だと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.08,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,どうせ遊んでばかりなんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.00,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,高木さんは  もう終わってそうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ううん  私も  あまりやってないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.47,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,人のこと言えないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.84,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:21.35,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,じゃ  あした  一緒に宿題やらない  図書館で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:23.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,決まりね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,終わったら  また神社  行こっか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.61,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.33,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,自由研究  どうするの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:53.09,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,夏休みの間に  西片を  からかったときの  リアクションまとめ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.05,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,…にしようと思ったけど  やめとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ホントにやめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.64,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.89,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  まだ全然  決まってなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.85,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっかぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.77,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,早く決めないと終わっちゃうね  夏休み
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.90,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  まだ半分  残ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.07,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,迷ってたら  あっという間だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:19.03,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:25.04,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,きっと  あっという間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.83,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの  この前…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:04.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.50,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  やっぱり  いい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.59,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.22,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとね  西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.60,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,助かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.26,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ…  うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:27.68,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,上がってく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:32.23,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いや  釣りの約束あるし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.73,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あっ  そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.40,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.37,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.99,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,西片?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:29.49,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あの  高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.55,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,な…  夏祭り…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.30,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,一緒に行かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:53.94,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:06.95,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,これもあげる  これも  これも  これも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.58,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいよ  こんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.70,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,いいから  いいから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.45,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,楽しみにしとくね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.11,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,次が大物だったら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.53,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,今日  北条さんを夏祭りに誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.32,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,小物だったら  あした  誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.66,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,誘うのは決まってんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.20,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,釣れなかったら  どうすんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.62,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お前  釣り  下手だし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.75,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,あさって  誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:02.46,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おい  西片  ジュースもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.92,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,おい  引いてるって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:06.97,Takagisan - text_jp,,0,0,0,,お〜い
